nce Search</a> by <a href=\"/Harm_Geert_Muller\" title=\"Harm Geert Muller\">Harm Geert Muller</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Category:The_Dorf\" title=\"Category:The Dorf\">The Dorf</a> feat. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/F.M._Einheit\">FM Einheit</a> und <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Caspar_Br%C3%B6tzmann\">Caspar Brötzmann</a> - <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Home_(Caspar_Br%C3%B6tzmann_Massaker_album)\">Massaker</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.grammatikoff.de/\">Grammatikoff</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Duisburg\">Duisburg</a>, May 17, 2014, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/MJVohz5k5_U?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=MVV-LVA&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Marc_Boul%C3%A9\" title=\"Marc Boulé\">Marc Boulé</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i>An FPGA Move Generator for the Game of Chess</i>. Masters thesis, <a href=\"/McGill_University\" title=\"McGill University\">McGill University</a>, (Supervisor: <a href=\"/Zeljko_Zilic\" title=\"Zeljko Zilic\">Zel